Generate 20 multiple-choice questions in JSON array format.

Requirements:
- Choose any subject (Science, Mathematics, English, Computer Science, General Knowledge, History, Geography, Islamic Studies, etc.).
- Each question must have exactly 4 options.
- Include the correct answer.
- Include a short explanation.
- Use this exact JSON structure:

[
  {
    "question": "Question text here?",
    "options": ["Option A", "Option B", "Option C", "Option D"],
    "correctAnswer": "Correct Option",
    "explanation": "Short explanation of the correct answer.",
    "subject": "Subject Name"
  }
]

Rules:
- Return only valid JSON.
- No markdown formatting.
- No additional text outside the JSON array.
- Questions should be educational and suitable for students.
- Ensure correctAnswer exactly matches one of the options.
- Subject can be any educational topic.